#note I failed to find the best pre-endgame here - I had the right idea, but in fact, if I find the best play Joanne will have a hard time winning the game, because I would've draw an out that she needed to block (DING). SKETTED is definitely superior, it blocks fewer column L bingos, but it also prevents her from bingoing to the -ED, and by playing an extra consonant and tile, it makes it more likely that I will draw an out in two spots.
